_text = "This specific year we turned the place into a witch inspired home. He spray foamed and then painted a bucket to make it look like a bubbling cauldron. He made over 30 'potions' using a variety of materials he found.\n\nI remember while decorating for this event, he forgot he was melting wax on the stove. He almost burned the whole house down that day. When we moved away there was still a huge burn mark up the wall behind the stove.\n\nHe was never bothered by any mistakes like this. He would just laugh about it and say he'd fix it later. He never did, but I learned from him to not stress over mistakes like these.\n\nDont let the fear of failure keep you from creating something."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, BasementRightMemory, BasementRightMemory, false)
